title: Can I still get Victorious Graves?
body:
Season ended on November 7 and pre-season started November 8.

Today I played my provisional games and I want to know if I'm still able to get Victorious Skin?

replies.body: Since the 2017 ranked stats were locked in at the end of Nov 7th, you can't get credit towards Victorious Graves for any progress after that point. Since you only recently played your provisionals after the season ended and you weren't ranked during the season, you won't be getting any of the rewards.

Eh, Graves was the face of season 7, and like you said it ended November 7, so you had to get at least Gold until that date.

Start playing for season 8!
